snippet.textDisplay:
I always come back to this video once a while, hoping to see a new upload from technoblade, but never will.

Although we are going to deal with many losses in our life, we instinctively wants to push that date further, hoping that it will not happen within our life time. Yet deep inside our heart, we have to accept the truth. 

I have always thought that life is too short, too short to make an impact, too short to achieve what you've desired, but Technoblade proved to me that although our life is as narrow as our hands, it can also be as vast as the morning sea, where waves continuously remind us of the treasurous moments of life.

Life is short, but your life has been an inspiration for many, including myself. Years after, when we look back at our achievements, we will be amazed at how far we've come, and what inspired us to do so. 

Rest in peace Technoblade, thank you for everything you've done.
